bug.short_desc: IE does not display some images (problem of AlphaImageLoader with https?)

long_desc.thetext:
It is no problem of the AlphaImageLoader with "https://".
Replace the url of the third button with e.g.
"https://s-static.ak.facebook.com/rsrc.php/v1/yp/r/kk8dc2UJYJ4.png"
and everything is working.
I can't also not reproduce this issue. I used IE9 and all images are loaded.
Closed all bugs already shipped with a release.
